<p class="basetext">Given the item's properties, information on the nature of SCP-042-IT must be filtered in the manner established by the D3EP-M1ND Protocol. Subjects exposed to SCP-042-IT-ψ without prior inoculation of the Klein-Mandelbrot memetic visual agent must be sedated and receive an Ω Class amnestic therapy (irreversible total amnesia). If they're confirmed to have been converted in SCP-042-IT-3 instances, they must be terminated.</p>

